%% Diagram: Inventory reservation lifecycle
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Available
    Available --> SoftReserved: Add to cart
    SoftReserved --> Available: TTL expires / item removed
    SoftReserved --> HardReserved: Payment authorized + saga commits
    HardReserved --> Allocated: Pick ticket created (warehouse)
    Allocated --> Shipped: Shipment dispatched
    HardReserved --> Available: Order cancelled (compensating action)
